    "- 注意 ray 以及 debugpy 的版本\n",
    "    - `pip show ray`\n",
    "    - `pip show debugpy`\n",
    "- slurm 集群\n",
    "    ```\n",
    "    ray start --head --ray-debugger-external --port 6379 --dashboard-host 0.0.0.0\n",
    "    ```\n",
    "    - 或者在配置 ray distributed debuger 时，用具体的计算节点的 ip 而不是 127.0.0.1"
   ]
  }
